Splitting Code in multiple Files
1. Writing a TS file and Compile it and manuall import the JS file in HTML --> not a good approch for Big Project
2. For bigger Project:
    a. NameSpace & File Bundling
        NameSpace is a TS feature which is a Special Syntax Feature which allows group the code into it and then import nameSpaces into other files
    
    b. ES6 Imports and Exports:
        TS supports ES6 Imports and Exports --> mordern Approach